## Root Cause
The mutation was built assuming a floraMeasurement union pattern. The ACTUAL lexicon at GENERATED/lexicons/app/gainforest/dwc/measurement.json uses simple DwC MeasurementOrFact fields:

Required: occurrenceRef, measurementType, measurementValue, createdAt
Optional: measurementID, occurrenceID, measurementUnit, measurementAccuracy, measurementMethod, measurementDeterminedBy, measurementDeterminedDate, measurementRemarks

There is NO 'result' field and NO 'floraMeasurement' union type in this lexicon.

## What to do

### 1. Update types.ts
Replace FloraMeasurementFields and CreateDwcMeasurementInput:
```ts
export type CreateDwcMeasurementInput = {
  occurrenceRef: string;       // AT-URI (required)
  measurementType: string;     // e.g. 'DBH', 'tree height', 'canopy cover' (required)
  measurementValue: string;    // e.g. '45.2', '12.5' (required)
  measurementUnit?: string;    // e.g. 'cm', 'm', '%'
  measurementID?: string;
  occurrenceID?: string;
  measurementAccuracy?: string;
  measurementMethod?: string;
  measurementDeterminedBy?: string;
  measurementDeterminedDate?: string;
  measurementRemarks?: string;
  rkey?: string;
};
```
Remove FloraMeasurementFields type from this file (it stays in bumicerts/lib/upload/types.ts for the UI layer).

### 2. Update create.ts
Build a simple record:
```ts
const candidate = {
  $type: COLLECTION,
  occurrenceRef: input.occurrenceRef,
  measurementType: input.measurementType,
  measurementValue: input.measurementValue,
  createdAt: new Date().toISOString(),
};
// Add optional fields only if defined
if (input.measurementUnit) candidate.measurementUnit = input.measurementUnit;
if (input.measurementID) candidate.measurementID = input.measurementID;
// ... etc for all optional fields
```
Remove all floraMeasurement/result logic.

### 3. Update index.ts
Remove FloraMeasurementFields from exports (it no longer exists in mutations-core). Update any changed type names.

### 4. Update UploadStep.tsx
Instead of creating one measurement record with a flora bundle, create N records (one per measurement field):
```ts
if (row.floraMeasurement) {
  const measurements: { type: string; value: string; unit: string }[] = [];
  if (row.floraMeasurement.dbh) measurements.push({ type: 'DBH', value: row.floraMeasurement.dbh, unit: 'cm' });
  if (row.floraMeasurement.totalHeight) measurements.push({ type: 'tree height', value: row.floraMeasurement.totalHeight, unit: 'm' });
  if (row.floraMeasurement.diameter) measurements.push({ type: 'basal diameter', value: row.floraMeasurement.diameter, unit: 'cm' });
  if (row.floraMeasurement.canopyCoverPercent) measurements.push({ type: 'canopy cover', value: row.floraMeasurement.canopyCoverPercent, unit: '%' });

  for (const m of measurements) {
    await createMeasurement.mutateAsync({
      occurrenceRef: occResult.uri,
      measurementType: m.type,
      measurementValue: m.value,
      measurementUnit: m.unit,
    });
  }
}
```

